            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF",
                "EDE",
                "TRN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The same particle upstream and downstream of the",
                "reaction target can be counted, and the reaction cross",
                "section is obtained by the transmission method."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The typical 14N primary beam intensity was about 20 nA",
                "on the production target of Be with 3123 um in",
                "thickness which was installed at the entrance of",
                "RIBLL. 12N and 12B were produced by the projectile",
                "fragmentation process."
              ]
            }
